      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project or a parts car. The exterior shows significant wear with several noticeable dents, rusted wheel arches, and fading paint across the hood and roof. Mechanically, it requires immediate attention as the engine runs roughly and the transmission exhibits slipping; additionally, the interior has heavy staining and a torn driver's seat. It is not currently in roadworthy condition and will need to be towed.",
